1
00:00:01,968 --> 00:00:03,269
You like me.

2
00:00:05,705 --> 00:00:06,406
If you say it that loud,

3
00:00:06,407 --> 00:00:07,707
it won't be a secret anymore.

4
00:00:08,775 --> 00:00:10,276
Why'd you write that anyway?

5
00:00:14,047 --> 00:00:16,082
That you like me.

6
00:00:20,153 --> 00:00:21,353
I always used to think

7
00:00:21,354 --> 00:00:22,489
you were cold,

8
00:00:22,822 --> 00:00:24,657
grumpy, and quiet.

9
00:00:25,191 --> 00:00:26,458
I didn't realize that in private,

10
00:00:26,459 --> 00:00:27,761
you're actually pretty normal.

11
00:00:28,261 --> 00:00:29,562
What's that supposed to mean?

12
00:00:32,932 --> 00:00:33,967
Just admit it.

13
00:00:34,667 --> 00:00:36,770
You're a fan of mine,

14
00:00:37,604 --> 00:00:38,705
aren't you?

15
00:00:39,752 --> 00:00:41,487
Is being a fan really that exciting?

16
00:00:42,108 --> 00:00:44,310
It's always nice to be appreciated.

17
00:00:44,844 --> 00:00:45,844
Come on, tell me.

18
00:00:45,912 --> 00:00:47,747
Are you a "White Rice Cake"?

19
00:00:49,149 --> 00:00:50,383
If you say so.

20
00:00:52,085 --> 00:00:52,786
Fine.

21
00:00:52,787 --> 00:00:55,053
I think you're actually a decent guy.

22
00:00:55,054 --> 00:00:56,188
Since we're partners now,

23
00:00:56,189 --> 00:00:58,191
let's put the past behind us.

24
00:00:59,059 --> 00:01:00,299
I never had a problem with you.

25
00:01:00,894 --> 00:01:02,362
Okay... fine, whatever.

26
00:01:03,563 --> 00:01:04,631
Let's get some sleep.

27
00:01:09,769 --> 00:01:10,503
Wait a second.

28
00:01:10,737 --> 00:01:12,571
Do you always get this
close to people so fast?

29
00:01:12,572 --> 00:01:13,306
You used to be

30
00:01:13,307 --> 00:01:14,908
so guarded around me.

31
00:01:16,042 --> 00:01:16,476
In the past,

32
00:01:16,477 --> 00:01:18,477
I didn't have many chances
to get close to people.

33
00:01:18,778 --> 00:01:19,412
And besides,

34
00:01:19,413 --> 00:01:20,813
your manager alone

35
00:01:20,814 --> 00:01:22,449
is enough to keep anyone away.

36
00:01:24,884 --> 00:01:25,885
Let's just sleep.

37
00:01:37,530 --> 00:01:39,299
They're still filming while we sleep.

38
00:01:39,632 --> 00:01:41,232
It's probably safer with the lights off.

39
00:01:41,935 --> 00:01:43,403
They have night vision, you know.

40
00:01:51,611 --> 00:01:52,891
Then what are we supposed to do?

41
00:01:55,115 --> 00:01:56,355
Well, since we're already here,

42
00:01:56,749 --> 00:01:58,383
and I know all your secrets,

43
00:01:58,384 --> 00:02:00,452
I could just

44
00:02:00,453 --> 00:02:02,020
take care of everything for you.

45
00:02:02,021 --> 00:02:03,021
Come here.

46
00:02:03,790 --> 00:02:04,790
In your dreams.

47
00:02:05,125 --> 00:02:06,925
You're just trying to
give them more footage.

48
00:02:10,997 --> 00:02:11,997
What?

49
00:02:15,168 --> 00:02:16,769
Don't go tossing and turning tonight.

50
00:02:17,504 --> 00:02:19,372
And don't try to feel me up.

51
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,240
Alright,

52
00:02:23,243 --> 00:02:24,444
let's just go to sleep.
